patthana16.27:1.1_0: Vipākaṁ hetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca navipāko nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.27:1.1_1: Vipākaṁ hetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca navipākadhammadhammo nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.27:1.1_2: Vipākaṁ hetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nanevavipākanavipākadhammadhammo nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.27:1.1_3: Vipākaṁ hetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca navipākadhammadhammo nahetu ca nanevavipākanavipākadhammadhammo nahetu ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā.
